>Description:
In a virgin DrScheme, choose

Help | About DrScheme | Release Notes ...

and nothing happens!  (There's a brief flutter, then nothing.)

If, however, the Help Desk is already open, then performing the above
operations results in the release notes becoming visible in the
open Help Desk window.  (I'm not sure I like this behavior either --
it'd be better if the Release Notes button always popped up
a new window, for various, obvious reasons.)

